## 7. Summary & Justification

- **Adapters decouple platform logic**; Discord/Facebook-specific logic never touches core parser/executor.
- **All workflows schema-driven**, hot-swappable without restarting the system.
- **Audit/versioning captures context**, platform, and resolution attempts.
- **Pluggable configuration** allows frictionless integration of new environments.
- **Discord and Facebook handled equally** with adaptive UI responses and platform-aware fallback.
- **Includes GUI and SDK demo code**: Agent GUI (Vite/React) and Discord SDK integration with slash command + modal fallback, Facebook thread support.

