This system delivers **modular, adaptive agent execution and input parsing** that scales from Discord to Facebook and beyond. With config-injected adapters, schema-driven workflows, and interface abstraction across environments, it forms a stable and extensible foundation for automation, assistants, or conversational agent platforms.

