Decide on a format for storing configurations, such as:

JSON: Commonly used for web applications.
{
  "triggerEvent": "userSignup",
  "userId": "12345",
  "commandType": "sendWelcomeEmail",
  "inputData": {
    "email": "user@example.com",
    "templateId": "welcome"
  },
  "targetAudience": ["groupID1", "groupID2"]
